race.comment: STARFIRE TEARS (1) boasts a consistent overall record including five wins from 14 starts, but missed the frame latest when fifth (43.19) over 730m at The Meadows. Has never missed the frame at the trip from four starts. Looks a key player drawing the cherry. HARA'S INDIANA (8) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth (25.92) in a Grade 5 at Q Lakeside. Worth another chance. AWAY DAYS (7) has a strong record this trip with four wins and two placings from 12 starts. Was out of placings last time (35.55) at this track in a Grade 4/5, finishing fourth and beaten 15 lengths. Among the main chances. LUMBY (4) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.
